title: The Pyramids are a Monument to Government Incompetence

media:group.media:title: The Pyramids are a Monument to Government Incompetence
media:group.media:description:
Monuments from the ancient world evoke awe and wonder, but their creation process isn’t as rosy. Would the past have been less crude if central dictate was replaced with decentralized creativity?
